creator: Rolf Boldrewood
description:
LibriVox recording of Plain Living by Rolf Boldrewood.
Read in English by VfkaBT
Seemingly down-on-his-luck Australian sheep rancher and orchard grower kindly teaches his loving family the value of money through 'plain living'. Fellow fans of Jon Cleary's "The Sundowners", set a generation later, may enjoy this. - Summary by Matt Pierard
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B Audiobook (219MB)
subject: librivox; audiobooks;romance; australia; 19th century; family values
title: Plain Living
